rows.label: qst700706_msg0001
rows.name:
Ah, sorry about that! I was trying to
warn you not to come any closer!

rows.label: qst700706_msg0002
rows.name:
I guess I need to get better at
warnings, huh... Sorry you got attacked.

rows.label: qst700706_msg0003
rows.name:
Anyway, it's been a while!
Didn't think I'd have to be saved by
you guys again, but here we are.

rows.label: qst700706_msg0004
rows.name:
You recognize me, right? It's Kaym.
Remember? You helped me with the
monster slash bridge situation?

rows.label: qst700706_msg0005
rows.name:
I had a feeling we'd bump into
each other again! Hahaha! What
a coincidence, eh?

rows.label: qst700706_msg0006
rows.name:
...Crud, I gotta hurry! Otherwise
my old man'll lay into me again!

rows.label: qst700706_msg0007
rows.name:
Sorry I have to dash!
Thanks for saving my skin!

rows.label: qst700706_msg0008
rows.name: I'll see you back in the capital!
